xum1541cfg: a configuration utility for the xum1541 Commodore floppy adapters
    By Nate Lawson <nate@root.org>
    ==============================

This utility will help you configure and update various xum1541 devices,
notably the ZoomFloppy. These devices connect a Commodore floppy drive
to a PC or Mac via USB so that files or entire disk images can be read and
written.


Compiling
===
* Linux, FreeBSD, or Mac OS X

    make -f LINUX/Makefile

* Windows

    Start up a DDK build prompt
    cd WINDOWS
    build /c


Usage
===
Run "xum1541cfg" without any arguments to get more info.
